1772820498112745	botbus-dev	itc:v3:AWLJMzzOef_QAAAAAAAAQdW3t3v_gAAAAAEpAg		item.create	bn-1fit	{"description":"botbus has been rebranded to rite. All references in edict's docs, protocol commands, and templates need updating.\n\n## What to rename\n- \"botbus\" → \"rite\" (package/project name)\n- \"bus\" when used as CLI command name (e.g., \"bus send\", \"bus inbox\") → \"rite\"\n- \"BotBus\" → \"Rite\" (capitalized in prose)\n- \"BOTBUS_\" env var prefix → \"RITE_\" (e.g., BOTBUS_AGENT → RITE_AGENT)\n- \"#botbus\" channel references → \"#rite\"\n- \"botbus-dev\" agent name → \"rite-dev\"\n- .botbus.toml → .rite.toml (if referenced)\n- ~/.local/share/botbus/ → ~/.local/share/rite/\n\n## Where to look\n- .agents/edict/*.md workflow docs (start, finish, worker-loop, triage, etc.)\n- Protocol output templates (the text emitted by `edict protocol start/review/finish/merge/cleanup`)\n- Any AGENTS.md template or scaffold code\n- README or other top-level docs\n- Source code strings that reference bus/botbus CLI commands\n\n## Context\n- The rite binary is now `rite` (was `bus`)\n- Env vars are RITE_AGENT, RITE_DATA_DIR, etc.\n- No backward compatibility needed","kind":"task","title":"Rename botbus/bus to rite in docs and protocol"}	blake3:UOCHfdEsrAmn6cZyq4g07Nru_ootOTVr2htXtVXGuUE
1772822666724732	botcrit-dev	itc:v3:AWLJJzk5yTmfxAAAAAAAQdV3XdXb-AAAAAEuAQ		item.create	bn-2ycm	{"description":"The crit project has been renamed to seal (github.com/bobisme/seal).\n\nAll references in edict docs, templates, and protocol files need to be updated:\n- 'crit' command → 'seal' command\n- 'botcrit' project name → 'botseal' (or just 'seal' where appropriate)\n- '.crit/' directory → '.seal/'\n- CRIT_AGENT → SEAL_AGENT, BOTCRIT_AGENT → BOTSEAL_AGENT\n- Any GitHub URLs pointing to botcrit → seal\n- Agent IDs like botcrit-dev, botcrit-security → botseal-dev, botseal-security\n- Bus channel references #botcrit → #botseal\n\nCheck .agents/edict/*.md, prompts/*.md, protocol files, and any templates that reference the review tool.","kind":"task","title":"Update all botcrit/crit references to seal"}	blake3:HWyGNOhinGxS57g7wtg8X5oZk_h8AlF5MSIWhNE1mLg
1772834281580593	edict-dev	itc:v3:AWLkkmTOfzk5kQAAAAAAQeqtbv7rtAAAAAEvAQ		item.move	bn-2ycm	{"state":"doing"}	blake3:kLFkYBeq2SvokTvX8Kk3XgJx3o72Kuv19ACfv5C7erY
